metadata.description:
we're back bitches
we made this 3/28/20 and it still fucks

after we made this one there was a moment of HOLY SHIT look what we did.. 
that hook.. (insert water squirt emoji) 
pulling the rest of the production straight out of our Skrillex handbook, we created Loose Ends

we love the juxtaposition of acoustic lofi and overly produced electronic rock. loose ends has always been one of our favorites and excited to see if this demo evolves into something even saucier. 

WHAT IS WORKS OF PROGRESS
we are tapping into our vault of early demos to release a series on sound.xyz... new drop every few weeks

some of these songs may evolve and be released traditionally and some not.. but these early versions will live forever on Sound and we love them.

one thing we’ve come to enjoy is while learning what this band is and how to make music for it, we made many “mistakes” sonically. we wanted to make big rock guitar sounds but had to learn how to do that first. In the tinkering and toying with sounds, sometimes something new would be created.. obstacles make opportunity and that is where the magic lies. 

here is loos ends.. the second of the works of progress series

lyrics.text:
tying up my loose ends again
you always find a new consequence
for something that i've done or that i've said
but what if it means nothing in the end...
